%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Israeli%20Air%20Force%20may%20have%20to%20think%20twice%20about%20taking%20on%20Hezbollah%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Israeli%20F-16I%20fighter%20flew%20over%20the%20border%20area%20with%20south%20Lebanon%20on%20March%2012%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66300803ec0c696569feef91%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20Israeli%20F-16I%20fighter%20flew%20over%20the%20border%20area%20with%20south%20Lebanon%20on%20March%2012%2C%202024.%3Cp%3EJalaa%20Marey%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHezbollah%20may%20have%20surface-to-air%20missiles%20than%20can%20threat%20Israeli%20aircraft.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20recent%20Israeli%20strike%20appears%20to%20have%20damaged%20a%20Iran-made%20Sayyad-2%20missile.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20possibility%20of%20missiles%20will%20%26quot%3Bforce%26quot%3B%20the%20IDF%20to%20be%20more%20cautious%20over%20Lebanon%2C%20an%20expert%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuch%20has%20been%20written%20about%20Hezbollah's%20enormous%20arsenal%20of%20surface-to-surface%20missiles%20and%20rockets%20and%20the%20devastation%20they%20could%20unleash%20against%20Israel.%20A%20recent%20incident%2C%20however%2C%20briefly%20put%20the%20spotlight%20on%20Hezbollah's%20lesser-known%20air%20defenses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20Israeli%20Air%20Force%20targeted%20Hezbollah%20sites%20south%20of%20the%20Lebanese%20city%20of%20Sidon%2C%20footage%20emerged%20purportedly%20showing%20the%20remains%20of%20an%20Iranian-built%20Sayyad-2%20surface-to-air%20missile.%20The%20Israeli%20military%20stated%20the%20Hezbollah%20sites%20targeted%20%26quot%3Bposed%20a%20threat%20to%20Israeli%20aircraft.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIsraeli%20media%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fliveblog_entry%2Fidf-strike-in-lebanon-seems-to-reveal-hezbollah-possesses-advanced-iranian-anti-aircraft-missiles%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20footage%20was%20%26quot%3Bapparently%20the%20first%20public%20evidence%20suggesting%20that%20Hezbollah%20has%20such%20missiles%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20had%20been%20previously%20claimed.%20Hezbollah%20has%20traded%20tit-for-tat%20strikes%20with%20Israel%20since%20Hamas'%20Oct.%207%20terror%20attacks%2C%20but%20the%20air%20defenses%20suggest%20Israel's%20Air%20Force%20would%20face%20a%20much%20greater%20threat%20over%20southern%20Lebanon%20than%20it%20has%20in%20Gaza's%20skies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Sayyad-2%20is%20a%20medium-range%20anti-aircraft%20missile%20Iran%20developed%20by%20heavily%20reverse%20engineering%20the%20American%20RIM-66%20Standard%20Missile%2C%20SM-1%2C%20Tehran%20acquired%20before%20the%201979%20revolution.%20The%20Sayyad-2%20has%20a%20shorter%20range%20than%20its%20successors.%20The%20most%20advanced%2C%20the%20Sayyad-4B%2C%20which%20Iran%20developed%20for%20its%20Bavar-373%20air%20defense%20system%2C%20has%20an%20estimated%20range%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.janes.com%2Fdefence-news%2Fnews-detail%2Firan-unveils-longer-range-sam%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E186%20miles%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20October%2C%20a%20Hezbollah-appointed%20guide%20showcased%20some%20of%20the%20group's%20firepower%20to%20visiting%20journalists%20and%20hinted%20they%20have%20long-range%20air%20defenses%20like%20the%20Russian%20S-300.%20%26quot%3BDo%20you%20think%20we%20don't%20have%20S-300%3F%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theglobeandmail.com%2Fworld%2Farticle-hezbollah-flaunts-its-firepower-as-tensions-mount-at-israel-lebanon%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%26quot%3BIf%20Iran%20has%20S-300%2C%20absolutely%20Hezbollah%20will%20take%20S-300.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20unclear%20if%20Iran%20has%20tried%20to%20transfer%20the%20Bavar-373%2C%20Iran's%20domestically-developed%20equivalent%20to%20the%20S-300%2C%20to%20Hezbollah%20with%20its%20Sayyad%204%2F4B%20missiles.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BHezbollah's%20air%20defense%20capabilities%20are%20very%20opaque%2C%26quot%3B%20Nicholas%20Blanford%2C%20a%20non-resident%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Atlantic%20Council%20and%20author%20of%20the%202011%20book%20%26quot%3BWarriors%20of%20God%3A%20Inside%20Hezbollah's%20Thirty-Year%20Struggle%20Against%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BMore%20is%20known%20about%20other%20systems%20in%20their%20arsenal%20than%20air%20defense%20because%20Hezbollah%20very%20rarely%20uses%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BNevertheless%2C%20if%20Iran%20possesses%20or%20can%20acquire%20an%20air%20defense%20system%20that%20suits%20Hezbollah's%20needs%2C%20then%20it%20is%20safe%20to%20assume%20that%20Hezbollah%20probably%20will%20have%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Blanford%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hezbollah%20expert%20also%20noted%20that%20possession%20of%20missiles%20like%20the%20Sayyad-2%20%26quot%3Bcertainly%20raises%20the%20threat%20level%26quot%3B%20to%20Israeli%20aircraft%20compared%20to%20shoulder-fired%20missiles.%20He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20Israel%20has%20%26quot%3Balways%20maintained%26quot%3B%20that%20any%20Hezbollah%20acquisition%20of%20advanced%20air%20defense%20systems%20amounts%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bred%20line.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%202013%2C%20Israel%20has%20sustained%20an%20air%20campaign%20in%20Syria%20targeting%20Iranian%20weapons%20shipments%20to%20Lebanon%20to%20prevent%20Hezbollah%20from%20acquiring%20high-end%20systems.%20It%20has%20intensified%20this%20campaign%20since%20the%20Hamas%2010%2F7%20attacks%2C%20likely%20making%20it%20more%20difficult%20than%20ever%20for%20Iran%20to%20transfer%20weapons%20to%20Hezbollah%20via%20Syria.%20During%20this%20campaign%2C%20Israeli%20jets%20have%20evaded%20and%2C%20at%20times%2C%20destroyed%20Syria's%20Russian-built%20short%20and%20medium-range%20Tor%20and%20Pantsir%20air%20defenses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20discovery%20of%20the%20Sayyad-2%20suggests%20Iran%20transferred%20at%20least%20some%20anti-aircraft%20missiles%20to%20its%20most%20valued%20regional%20proxy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20reported%20that%20Hezbollah%20possesses%20Sayyad-2%20anti-aircraft%20missiles%20previously%2C%20and%20the%20Israeli%20strike%20on%20Friday%20solidified%20those%20claims%2C%26quot%3B%20Freddy%20Khoueiry%2C%20a%20global%20security%20analyst%20for%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20North%20Africa%20at%20the%20risk%20intelligence%20company%20RANE%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20suspected%20that%20Hezbollah%20has%20been%20using%20the%20Sayyad-2%20to%20shoot%20down%20some%20of%20Israel's%20advanced%20Hermes%20900%20drones%20over%20Lebanon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BHezbollah%20has%20for%20the%20past%20few%20years%20boasted%20of%20advancing%20its%20air-defensive%20capabilities%2C%20and%20the%20discovery%20of%20Hezbollah's%20possession%20of%20Sayyad-2%20demonstrates%20how%20much%20they%20obtained%20advanced%20anti-air%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20Khoueiry%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Israeli%20F-35%20stealth%20fighter%20flew%20over%20the%20border%20area%20with%20south%20Lebanon%20on%20March%2012%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66522f5920abc1efe8fdbc5f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20Israeli%20F-35%20stealth%20fighter%20flew%20over%20the%20border%20area%20with%20south%20Lebanon%20on%20March%2012%2C%202024.%3Cp%3EJalaa%20Marey%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIsrael%20has%20experience%20destroying%20formidable%20air%20defenses%20in%20Lebanon.%20When%20it%20invaded%20the%20country%20in%201982%2C%20it%20launched%20a%20coordinated%2C%20large-scale%20suppression%20of%20enemy%20air%20defense%20operation%20against%20an%20array%20of%20Soviet-built%20surface-to-air%20missile%20batteries%20Syria%20had%20deployed%20to%20Lebanon's%20Bekaa%20Valley.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOperation%20Mole%20Cricket%2019%20obliterated%20the%20Syrian%20missiles%20and%20saw%20Israel's%20new%20F-15%20and%20F-16%20fighters%20dogfight%20the%20Syrian%20Air%20Force%2C%20shooting%20down%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airandspaceforces.com%2Farticle%2F0602bekaa%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E82%20Syrian%20aircraft%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20without%20losing%20a%20single%20fighter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Hezbollah%20is%20unlikely%20ever%20to%20field%20a%20network%20of%20anti-aircraft%20missiles%20that%20large%2C%20some%20of%20its%20air%20defenses%20could%20nevertheless%20impact%20Israeli%20air%20operations%20over%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BGenerally%20speaking%2C%20this%20will%20unlikely%20deter%20Israel's%20Air%20Force%20from%20operating%20over%20Lebanon%20but%20will%20likely%20force%20the%20Israelis%20to%20become%20more%20cautious%20amid%20Hezbollah's%20changing%20tactics%20and%20their%20more%20advanced%20capabilities%2C%20such%20as%20having%20their%20fighter%20jets%20flying%20at%20higher%20altitudes%20or%20using%20stealthier%20jets%20like%20the%20F-35%2C%26quot%3B%20Khoueiry%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIsrael's%20Air%20Force%20is%20much%20more%20advanced%20and%20can%20bypass%20these%20air%20defenses%2C%20maintaining%20its%20immense%20air%20superiority%2C%20but%20Israeli%20drones%20and%20helicopters%20operating%20over%20Lebanon%20could%20be%20more%20at%20risk%2C%20especially%20if%20the%20IDF%20expands%20its%20operations%20in%20Lebanon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhoueiry%20doubts%20Iran%20will%20transfer%20strategic%20systems%20like%20the%20Bavar-373%20to%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20more%20likely%20that%20Iran%20can%20and%20did%20transfer%20medium-sized%20and%20range%20defensive%20systems%20to%20Hezbollah%2C%26quot%3B%20Khoueiry%20said.%20%26quot%3BLarger%20anti-air%20defense%20systems%20like%20the%20Bavar-373%20are%20harder%20to%20transfer%20given%20their%20size%2C%20but%20also%20given%20that%20Lebanon's%20geography%20is%20small%20and%20Hezbollah%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20properly%20operate%20them%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20RANE%20analyst%20believes%20that%20if%20Iran%20did%20deploy%20the%20Bavar-373%20in%20the%20region%2C%20it%20would%20send%20it%20somewhere%20like%20Syria%2C%20although%20he%20estimates%20that's%20unlikely%20at%20this%20point.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20discovery%20of%20the%20Sayyad-2%20likely%20hints%20that%20Iran%20has%20been%20able%20to%20transfer%20more%20similar%20advanced%20defensive%20systems%20that%20Hezbollah%20is%20likely%20to%20use%20in%20a%20progressive%20way%20as%20the%20conflict%20escalates%20or%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20wider%20war%2C%20especially%20given%20the%20likely%20limited%20number%20they%20possess%2C%26quot%3B%20Khoueiry%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisraeli-air-force-has-to-think-twice-about-hezbollah-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716710401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66522d4020abc1efe8fdbc53%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busi