raction%20themed%20around%20the%20ship%20is%20located%2C%20prompting%20one%20reporter%20to%20ask%20if%20he%20is%20%26quot%3Bcaptaining%20a%20sinking%20ship%20going%20into%20this%20election%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20Labour%20leader%20Keir%20Starmer%20is%20also%20in%20full%20campaign%20swing%20planning%20to%20use%20the%20day%20at%20public%20events%20designed%20to%20focus%20on%20his%20argument%20that%20the%20Conservatives%20have%20damaged%20the%20economy%20and%20raised%20living%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20came%20as%20Labour's%20lead%20fell%20by%20three%20points%20in%20the%20first%20YouGov%20opinion%20poll%20since%20Rishi%20Sunak%20called%20the%20snap%20summer%20general%20election%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%2C%20conducted%20on%20Thursday%20and%20Friday%2C%20shows%20the%20Conservatives%20up%20by%20one%20point%20to%2022%20per%20cent%2C%20while%20Labour%20is%20down%20two%20to%2044%20per%20cent.%20PTI%20AK%20GSP%20AKJ%20GSP%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716706320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F4ik9rkn4_rishi-sunak-reuters_625x300_25_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fuk-pm-rishi-sunak-faces-mass-exodus-of-mp-ahead-of-july-4-election-5742284%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20declaring%20a%20general%20election%20for%20July%204%2C%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20is%20reportedly%20spending%20his%20first%20Saturday%20with%20his%20closest%20advisers%20as%20he%20takes%20an%20%26quot%3Bunusual%20step%26quot%3B%20of%20a%20day%20away%20from%20public%20events.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fuk-pm-rishi-sunak-faces-mass-exodus-of-mp-ahead-of-july-4-election-5742284%22%2C%22cdnAmp