d%20boos%20and%20jeers.%20A%20smaller%20section%20of%20the%20crowd%2C%20Trump%20supporters%2C%20cheered%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20before%20he%20appeared%2C%20one%20Libertarian%20Party%20member%20shouted%3A%20%26quot%3BDonald%20Trump%20should%20have%20taken%20a%20bullet!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20campaign%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20about%20the%20hostile%20reception.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20who%20was%20president%20between%202017%20and%202021%2C%20immediately%20mentioned%20the%20total%2088%20felony%20charges%20he%20faces%20in%20four%20federal%20and%20state%20prosecutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20wasn't%20a%20libertarian%20I%20am%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20denounced%20the%20administration%20of%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20his%20challenger%20in%20the%20Nov.%205%20election%20rematch%2C%20and%20Biden's%20fellow%20Democrats%20as%20being%20part%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Brise%20in%20left-wing%20fascism%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20was%20trying%20to%20appeal%20to%20libertarians%2C%20who%20have%20more%20in%20common%20with%20Republican%20policy%20positions%20than%20Democrats%20on%20issues%20including%20taxes%20and%20the%20size%20of%20government%2C%20in%20what%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20a%20closely%20fought%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20should%20not%20be%20fighting%20each%20other.%26quot%3B%20He%20asked%20libertarians%20to%20work%20with%20him%20to%20defeat%20Biden%2C%20an%20appeal%20which%20was%20greeted%20by%20many%20boos%2C%20although%20the%20vast%20majority%20in%20the%20crowd%20were%20fiercely%20opposed%20to%20Biden%20and%20his%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELibertarians%20garnered%20only%201.2%25%20of%20the%20national%20vote%20in%202020%2C%20or%20about%201.8%20million%20votes%2C%20but%20November's%20election%20could%20be%20decided%20by%20just%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20votes%20in%20a%20handful%20of%20battleground%20states%2C%20so%20Trump%20is%20seeking%20to%20peel%20away%20some%20libertarian%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20appearance%20at%20the%20libertarian%20gathering%2C%20unusual%20for%20a%20Republican%20White%20House%20candidate%2C%20also%20signaled%20how%20seriously%20he%20and%20his%20campaign%20take%20the%20threat%20of%20third-party%20candidate%20Robert%20F.%20Kennedy%20Jr.%2C%20who%20has%20long%20opposed%20vaccines%20and%20mandates%2C%20and%20who%20spoke%20to%20the%20convention%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20been%20ramping%20up%20attacks%20on%20Kennedy%2C%20who%20is%20running%20as%20an%20independent%2C%20recently%20calling%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bfake%26quot%3B%20anti-vaccination%20proponent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpinion%20polls%20suggest%20Kennedy%20will%20siphon%20votes%20away%20from%20both%20Trump%20and%20Biden%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20yet%20clear%20which%20of%20the%20major-party%20candidates%20will%20be%20hurt%20more%20by%20Kennedy's%20long-shot%20White%20House%20bid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELibertarian%20Party%20organizers%20said%20Biden%20was%20also%20invited%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20convention%20but%20he%20declined%20to%20attend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Libertarian%20Party%20can%20make%20a%20big%20difference.%20If%20we%20unite%20we%20will%20be%20unstoppable%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20to%20a%20mix%20of%20applause%20and%20jeers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20said%20he%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Blibertarian%20without%20even%20trying%20to%20be%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20Libertarian%20Party%20should%20endorse%20him%2C%20another%20line%20greeted%20by%20boos%20and%20jeers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUndeterred%2C%20Trump%20poked%20fun%20at%20the%20crowd%2C%20saying%20if%20they%20did%20not%20back%20him%2C%20they%20would%20continue%20to%20garner%20just%20a%20tiny%20portion%20of%20voter%20support%20in%20national%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20pledged%20to%20put%20a%20libertarian%20in%20his%20cabinet%20if%20he%20wins%20the%20election%2C