%20was%20packed%20with%20visitors%20due%20to%20a%20weekend%20discount%20offer%20with%20tickets%20priced%20at%20just%20Rs%2099.%20It%20is%20suspected%20that%20the%20fire%20might%20have%20started%20due%20to%20a%20short%20circuit%2C%20but%20officials%20said%20that%20the%20exact%20cause%20will%20be%20known%20only%20after%20a%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20for%20the%20fire%20has%20yet%20to%20be%20ascertained.%20The%20attempts%20to%20douse%20the%20fire%20are%20underway.%20We%20are%20facing%20difficulty%20in%20the%20firefighting%20operation%20because%20the%20temporary%20structure%20has%20collapsed%20and%20also%20due%20to%20the%20wind%20velocity%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20fire%20department%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intensity%20of%20the%20fire%20was%20such%20that%20smoke%20was%20visible%20from%20several%20kilometers%20away.%20The%20bodies%20were%20charred%20beyond%20recognition%2C%20officials%20said.%20The%20DNA%20samples%20of%20the%20bodies%20and%20the%20victim's%20relatives%20have%20been%20collected%20for%20identification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideos%2Fembed-player%2F%3Fid%3D788161%26mute%3D1%26autostart%3D1%26mutestart%3Dtrue%26pWidth%3D100%26pHeight%3D100%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20gaming%20zone%20did%20not%20possess%20the%20necessary%20licences%20to%20operate%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20record%20of%20a%20no-objection%20certificate%20(NOC)%20for%20fire%20clearance%20from%20the%20Rajkot%20Municipal%20Corporation.%20This%20lack%20of%20regulatory%20compliance%20has%20come%20under%20sharp%20scrutiny%20following%20the%20disaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajkot%20Mayor%20Nayna%20Pedhadiya%2C%20who%20arrived%20at%20the%20scene%20to%20oversee%20the%20rescue%20operations%2C%20confirmed%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20fire%20NOC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20investigate%20how%20such%20a%20big%20game%20zone%20was%20functioning%20without%20a%20fire%20NOC%20and%20we%20are%20witnessing%20the%20consequences%20of%20it.%20No%20politics%20will%20be%20allowed%20over%20this%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Pedhadiya%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20facility%20also%20had%20just%20one%20emergency%20exit%20and%20there%20was%20panic%20after%20the%20fire%20broke%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20got%20trapped%20as%20a%20temporary%20structure%20at%20the%20facility%20collapsed%20near%20the%20entrance%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20the%20people%20to%20come%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Rajkot%20fire%20officer%20Ilesh%20Kher%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20owner%20and%20manager%20of%20the%20TRP%20game%20zone%20have%20been%20detained%20for%20questioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20fire%20tragedy%2C%20the%20state%20director%20general%20of%20police%20has%20issued%20instructions%20to%20the%20commissioners%20of%20police%20and%20superintendents%20of%20police%20to%20inspect%20all%20the%20game%20zones%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20close%20those%20running%20without%20fire%20safety%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DGP%20has%20directed%20the%20police%20to%20carry%20out%20this%20procedure%20in%20coordination%20with%20fire%20officers%20of%20the%20municipalities%20and%20municipalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716703680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fs96up1ng_rajkot-gaming-zone-fire_625x300_26_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajkot-fire-live-updates-no-fire-license-one-exit-major-safety-violations-at-rajkot-game-zone-5747655%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20massive%20fire%20at%20a%20gaming%20zone%20in%20Rajkot%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20death%20of%2028%20people%2C%20including%209%20children%2C%20has%20raised%20serious%20questions%20about%20the%20safety%20standards%20at%20the%20facility.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%