le%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20or%20end%20reservation%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV.%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20had%20changed%20the%20Preamble%20in%201976%2C%20but%20is%20now%20trying%20to%20unnecessarily%20target%20the%20BJP%20and%20make%20it%20a%20poll%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%201976%2C%20the%20first%20time%20a%20change%20was%20made%20to%20the%20Preamble%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution.%20And%20that%20was%20done%20by%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20our%20constituent%20assembly%20was%20then%20of%20the%20consensus%20that%20amendments%20can%20be%20made%20to%20the%20Constitution%20as%20required.%20Congress%20and%20other%20political%20parties%20have%20done%20this%20a%20lot.%20But%20there%20is%20no%20question%20of%20making%20changes%20in%20the%20preamble.%20But%20they%20did%20it%2C%20and%20are%20now%20trying%20to%20blame%20us.%20The%20BJP%20does%20not%20even%20think%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajnath%20Singh's%20remarks%20come%20after%20claims%20by%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20%26quot%3Btear%20up%20and%20throw%20away%26quot%3B%20the%20Constitution%20if%20it%20retains%20power.%20Some%20other%20Congress%20functionaries%20had%20expressed%20apprehensions%20that%20the%20BJP%20may%20drop%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bsecularism%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20Preamble%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20also%20said%20that%20the%20ruling%20party%20has%20no%20plans%20of%20ending%20caste-based%20reservation%2C%20but%20will%20never%20give%20reservation%20based%20on%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20would%20we%20end%20reservation%3F%20This%20country%20needs%20reservation%20for%20OBC%2C%20ST.%20They%20(Opposition)%20are%20the%20ones%20talking%20about%20giving%20reservations%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion.%20But%20we%20say%20that%20in%20no%20situation%20will%20we%20give%20religion-based%20reservation%20as%20the%20Constitution%20does%20not%20allow%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Defence%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20is%20hoping%20to%20win%20their%20third%20ongoing%20term.%20Six%20of%20the%20seven%20phases%20of%20voting%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20have%20already%20been%20held%2C%20with%20results%20to%20be%20announced%20on%20June%204%20after%20the%20final%20round%20of%20voting%20on%20June%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716703320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fbq5oplh8_rajnath-singh-ndtv_625x300_26_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findira-gandhi-first-changed-the-preamble-bjp-would-never-rajnath-singh-to-ndtv-5748040%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20will%20never%20change%20the%20Preamble%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20or%20end%20reservation%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findira-gandhi-first-changed-the-preamble-bjp-would-never-rajnath-singh-to-ndtv-5748040%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findira-gandhi-first-changed-the-preamble-bjp-would-never-rajnath-singh-to-ndtv-5748040%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findira-gandhi-first-changed-the-preamble-bjp-would-never-rajnath-singh-to-ndtv-5748040%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Don't%20be%20surprised%E2%80%A6'%3A%20Ex-India%20player%20on%20possible%20outcome%20of%20IPL%20final%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716703111000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110434415%2Cimgsize-125962.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22