of%20windows%20to%20escape%20the%20inferno%20that%20swept%20through%20a%20centre%20packed%20full%20of%20young%20people%20enjoying%20games%20including%20bowling%2C%20media%20reported%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELines%20of%20bodies%20draped%20in%20white%20cloths%20were%20laid%20out%20before%20being%20taken%20away%20from%20the%20centre%20in%20Rajkot%20in%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20children%20reported%20dead%20were%20all%20aged%20under%2012%2C%20said%20police%2C%20who%20warned%20that%20many%20of%20the%20corpses%20were%20so%20badly%20burned%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20identify%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20300%20people%20were%20enjoying%20the%20summer%20holiday%20weekend%20in%20the%20two-storey%20structure%20at%20the%20TRP%20amusement%20and%20theme%20park%20when%20the%20blaze%20broke%20out%20on%20Saturday%20evening%2C%20Rajkot%20fire%20officer%20Ilesh%20Kher%20told%20reporters%20on%20the%20night%20of%20the%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20got%20trapped%20as%20a%20temporary%20structure%20at%20the%20facility%20collapsed%20near%20the%20entrance%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20the%20people%20to%20come%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flames%20spread%20rapidly%20because%20of%20the%20structure's%20flammable%20material%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E'Tried%20to%20escape'%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20confirmed%20the%20death%20of%2027%20persons%20in%20the%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20police%20officer%20Radhika%20Bharai%20told%20reporters%20overnight%2C%20updating%20an%20earlier%20toll%20of%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bodies%20are%20charred%20beyond%20recognition%20and%20hence%20their%20identification%20is%20difficult.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20officers%20warned%20the%20toll%20may%20rise%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurvivors%20recalled%20their%20horror%20as%20they%20struggled%20to%20flee%20the%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20bowlin