s%20brain%20dead.%20An%20autopsy%20showed%20that%20she%20died%C2%A0from%20a%20diabetes-related%20brain%20injury%20and%20being%20fed%20a%20sugary%20drink%20through%20a%20bottle%20that%20dissolved%20her%20teeth.%20She%20was%20never%20taken%20to%20the%20dentist%2C%20the%20paper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20also%20pointed%20out%20Banks%20has%20several%20other%20grown%20children%20who%20were%20treated%20poorly%20in%20her%20custody%2C%20including%20a%20son%20who%20fell%20into%20a%20coma%20at%204%20years%20old%20from%20previously%20undiagnosed%20diabetes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Banks%20regularly%20refilled%20her%20prescriptions%20and%20even%20had%20doctors%20visit%20her%20apartment%20to%20ensure%20that%20her%20medical%20needs%20were%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20to%20be%20a%20good%20parent%20but%20you%20expect%20at%20least%20mediocre%20parents%2C%20everybody%20should%20expect%20that.%20Not%20knowing%20what%20to%20do%20is%20not%20an%20excuse%2C%20the%20judge%20said%20during%20Friday's%20hearing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Ohio%20state%20law%2C%20Banks%20could%20serve%20as%20much%20as%2013%20and%20a%20half%20years%20if%20the%20Department%20of%20Rehabilitation%20and%20Correction%20decides%20to%20extend%20her%20sentence%20based%20on%20behaviour%20while%20jailed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716699420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F6eqbamlg_karmity-hoeb_625x300_26_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-jailed-for-killing-her-daughter-4-by-feeding-her-diet-of-mountain-dew-5747535%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prosecutors%20said%20Tamara%20Banks%20caused%20her%20daughter's%20death%20through%20malnutrition%20and%20lack%20of%20proper%20medical%20care.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-jailed-for-killing-her-daughter-4-by-feeding-her-diet-of-mountain-dew-57475