E%26quot%3BThe%20recognition%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20state%20by%20a%20number%20of%20European%20countries%20is%20a%20great%20loss%20for%20the%20occupation%2C%26quot%3B%20Middle%20East%20Monitor%20cited%20him%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20recognition%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20results%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BAl-Aqsa%20Flood%20battle%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20October%207%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20results%20of%20the%20Al-Aqsa%20Flood%20and%20the%20steadfastness%20of%20the%20resistance%20is%20that%20today%20Israel%20is%20appearing%20before%20the%20ICC%20(International%20Criminal%20Court)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENasrallah%20accused%20Israel%20of%20not%20respecting%20international%20resolutions%20and%20launching%20violent%20raids%20on%20Rafah%20despite%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20(ICJ)%20order%20to%20immediately%20halt%20its%20military%20offensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHanegbi%2C%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu's%20top%20aide%2C%20had%20said%20after%20the%20ICJ%20ruling%20that%20his%20country%20has%20the%20right%20to%20defend%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716696900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fbiac7msg_hassan-nasrallah_625x300_26_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhezbollahs-hassan-nasrallah-warns-israel-of-surprises-as-gaza-conflict-keeps-raging-5747318%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20the%20Gaza%20conflict%20still%20raging%20in%20its%20eighth%20month%2C%20Iran-backed%20Lebanese%20outfit%20Hezbollah%20is%20reportedly%20preparing%20for%20a%20surprise%20attack%20on%20Israel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhezbollahs-hassan-nasrallah-warns-israel-of-surprises-as-gaza-conflict-keeps-raging-5747318%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.or