njoy%20the%20thrilling%20finale.%20The%20cricket%20pitch%20along%20with%20a%20giant%20ball%2C%20bat%20and%20stumps%20are%20also%20seen%20in%20the%20doodle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20its%20doodle%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoodles.google%2Fdoodle%2F2024-indian-premier-league-final%2F%5C%22%3EGoogle%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20''This%20Doodle%20celebrates%20the%20final%20match%20of%20the%202024%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20season%2C%20also%20known%20as%20IPL17%20or%20TATA%20IPL%202024%2C%20taking%20place%20in%20Chennai.%20This%20year's%20tournament%20has%20been%20brimming%20with%20excitement%2C%20and%20many%20are%20eager%20to%20see%20which%20team%20will%20be%20crowned%20champion.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20tournament%20started%20with%20ten%20teams%20from%20all%20over%20India%20split%20into%20two%20different%20groups.%20Every%20team%20played%20a%20total%20of%2014%20games--seven%20home%20and%20seven%20away.%20After%20the%20group%20stage%2C%20the%20top%20four%20teams%20advanced%20to%20the%20high-stakes%20Qualifier%20and%20Eliminator%20stages.%20Through%20perseverance%20and%20teamwork%2C%20both%20teams%20have%20come%20out%20on%20top%20to%20face%20off%20in%20the%20IPL17%20finals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20IPL%20Eliminator%2C%20SRH%20defeated%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20and%20the%20Pat%20Cummins-led%20side%20followed%20it%20up%20with%20a%20comprehensive%20victory%20over%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20in%20IPL%20Qualifier%202%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20topped%20the%20league%20stages%20with%2019%20points%20and%20then%20defeated%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20in%20Qualifier%201%20to%20comfortably%20book%20their%20spot%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%20final.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it%20has%20been%20a%20tough%20road%20for%20SRH%20who%20finished%20third%20in%20the%20points%20table%20despite%20showing%20a%20good%20run%20of%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20a%20Google%20Doodle%20is%20a%20thematic%20motif%20that%20is%20used%20by%20the%20search%20engine%20on%20its%20homepage%20to%20mark%20special%20occasions.%20Google%20has%20also%20used%20doodles%20to%20celebrate%20prominent%20people%2C%20their%20achievements%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716694740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Ftf69ut7o_google-doodle_625x300_26_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fgoogle-celebrates-2024-indian-premier-league-final-with-a-vibrant-doodle-5747278%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22IPL%20Final%202024%3A%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20are%20all%20set%20to%20take%20on%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20(SRH)%20at%20MA%20Chidambaram%20Stadium%20in%20Chennai.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fgoogle-celebrates-2024-indian-premier-league-final-with-a-vibrant-doodle-5747278%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fgoogle-celebrates-2024-indian-premier-league-final-with-a-vibrant-doodle-5747278%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fgoogle-celebrates-2024-indian-premier-league-final-with-a-vibrant-doodle-5747278%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cyclone%20Remal%20Landfall%20Likely%20In%20Bengal%20Today%2C%20Flight%20Ops%20To%20Be%20Hit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwest-bengal-braces-for-cyclone-remal-dos-and-donts-to-stay-safe-5735226%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECyclone%20Remal%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20expected%20to%20make%20landfall%20between%20West%20Bengal's%20Sagar%20Island%20and%20Bangladesh's%20Khepupara%20at%20midnight%20on%20Sunday%2C%20according%20to%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERemal%20was%20centered%20about%20290%20km%20south-southeast%20of%20Sagar%20Island%20and%20300%20km%20south-southwest%20of