C%20the%20farm%20always%20had%20an%20audience.%20People%20were%20intrigued%20at%20how%20the%20father-son%20duo%20had%20created%20a%20yellow%20oasis%2C%20and%20the%20organic%20methods%20they%20had%20used%20to%20achieve%20the%20feat.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20many%20guests%20who%20wanted%20to%20observe%20how%20we%20were%20preparing%20our%20organic%20fertilisers%20from%20cow%20dung%20(we%20had%2035%20cows%20in%20our%20shed)%2C%20how%20we%20used%20neem%20to%20make%20our%20pesticides%2C%20and%20how%20our%20mangoes%20were%20thriving%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ganesh%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-5-1715946632.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Ganesh%20Agro%20Tourism%20homestay%20lies%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20Ratnagiri%20and%20Sindhudurg%20districts%20of%20Maharashtra%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-5-1715946632.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-5-1715946632-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-5-1715946632-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-5-1715946632-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-5-1715946632-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350407%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Ganesh%20Agro%20Tourism%20homestay%20lies%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20Ratnagiri%20and%20Sindhudurg%20districts%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Ganesh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%